## Troubleshooting

### iOS

```bash
# Clean build
cd ios
rm -rf build
pod deintegrate && pod install

# Reset simulator
xcrun simctl erase all
```

### Android

```bash
# Clean build
cd android
./gradlew clean

# Clear cache
rm -rf ~/.gradle/caches/
```

### Metro Bundler

```bash
# Reset cache
npm start -- --reset-cache

# Kill port 8081
lsof -ti:8081 | xargs kill
```

